Apollo International Ltd: Company Profile - Bloomberg




































































  









Feedback























apollo international ltd
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Other Commercial Services
Apollo International Limited (AIL) operates as a multidimensional organization. The Company business areas includes integrated logistics solutions, marketing and distribution of tires, tubes, flaps and rims, and manufacturing and export of leather garment and accessories. AIL conducts business worldwide.




