Apollo Management International LLP: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 26, 2017 3:49 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Apollo Management International LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Apollo Management International LLP is a private equity firm specializing in growth, buyout, mezzanine, turnaround, and fund of fund investments. The firm prefers to invest in all business lines. It usually invests in companies with minimum revenue of €1 billion. It seeks to invest worldwide. Apollo Management International LLP is based in London, United Kingdom and has additional offices in the United States, Europe, and Asia.


25 Saint George StreetLondon,  W1S1FSUnited Kingdom



Phone: 44 20 7016 5000

Fax: 44 20 79997712

www.agm.com







